title: Floor Lamps
body: Eye-catching floor lamps that were inspired by the greatest designs of the 20th century Bauhaus, this and more other wide selection of lightning accessories by Mobelaris. We are dedicated to bring quality style of Scandinavian and contemporary mid-century design furniture with a twist of modern touch to the public at incredibly low prices. We cut the involvement of middlemen and work directly to manufacturer’s so you can get the best style designs to suit your décor without having to pay too much. At Mobelaris, we make premium style furniture accessible for every home.
